  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Ranton Clan, Level 4+</p><p>You learn to more masterfully control Storm Release. <br />You gain the following Benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Increase your Dexterity or Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20. </p><p><br />• Once per turn, when you would cast a Ranton clan Hijutsu, you can conjure a source of water that fill a space that can hold it. This source of water can be used to cast Ninjutsu with the Water release keyword. </p><p>• Ranton Hijutsu you cast reduces their cost by an amount equal to their rank. (D-Rank: 1, C-Rank: 2, B-Rank: 3, A-Rank: 4, S-Rank: 5.)</p>",
